62-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Shen_Kuo#cite_ref-restivo_1992_32_62-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-restivo_1992_32-62" class="mw-reference-text">Restivo (1992), 32.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-katz_2007_308_309-63" id="cite_note-katz_2007_308_309-63"><a href="./Shen_Kuo#cite_ref-katz_2007_308_309_63-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-katz_2007_308_309-63" class="mw-reference-text">Katz (2007), 308–309.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-katz_2007_309-64" id="cite_note-katz_2007_309-64"><a href="./Shen_Kuo#cite_ref-katz_2007_309_64-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-katz_2007_309-64" class="mw-reference-text">Katz (2007), 309.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-sivin_1995_III_12_14-65" id="cite_note-sivin_1995_III_12_14-65"><a href="./Shen_Kuo#cite_ref-sivin_1995_III_12_14_65-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-sivin_1995_III_12_14-65" class="mw-reference-text">Sivin (1995), III, 12, 14.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-sivin_1995_III_14-66" id="cite_note-sivin_1995_III_14-66"><a href="./Shen_Kuo#cite_ref-sivin_1995_III_14_66-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-sivin_1995_III_14-66" class="mw-reference-text">Sivin (1995), III, 14.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-ebrey_2006_162-67" id="cite_note-ebrey_2006_162-67"><a href="./Shen_Kuo#cite_ref-ebrey_2006_162_67-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-ebrey_2006_162-67" class="mw-reference-text">Ebrey et al. (2006), 162.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-68" id="cite_note-68"><a href="./Shen_Kuo#cite_ref-68" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <sp